===Noun===
'''Proto-Greek'''
# The earliest form of the [[Greek]] [[language]], the [[common ancestor]] of the Greek [[dialect]]s, including [[Mycenean]] and the classical Greek dialects, spoken by the ancestors of the Greeks even before the settled in [[Greece]] around 2000 BC.

